Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在离开此入门部分之前，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我给你八个快速考虑如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际参加这门课程。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证他们是超级短的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且超级重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请，请不要跳过这个视频。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将为您在本课程中取得成功做好准备。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以开始，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能这是您的第一次接触
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与编写代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请不要不知所措。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的看到成千上万的学生去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过本课程或我的其他课程之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以告诉你这是100%正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始你不会真正理解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，请继续阅读前几节。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你一开始没有百分百了解，
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很快就会的，相信我。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很正常。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不要想像，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜编码不适合我。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，这里根本不允许这种想法。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要记住，每个人都有不同的学习
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你最终会到达那里，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续关注课程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并尽可能多地练习。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在关于实际参加课程。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是，总是需要和我一起编码。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对是根本性的。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您将通过简单地学习完全零 HTML 和 CSS 技能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在那里看着我写代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你真的必须自己写代码，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使您只是输入与我完全相同的单词
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上是在视频中打字，但这并不重要。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在编码，
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代码正在进入你的大脑，你正在学习。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这才是最重要的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想让课程材料留在你的大脑中，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更好的是，然后做笔记。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以关于代码语法的注释，关于理论概念的注释，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并真正注意一切。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能记太多笔记。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，每个人都有自己的风格。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只需要找到你自己的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来，尝试我向您展示的所有编码挑战。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽力做到最好，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你因为某种原因卡得太久，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续看解决方案。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须尝试编码挑战。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你会错过很多学习机会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里，也不要打败自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想不出解决办法。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次，这是完全正常的，
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是如果你只是一个初学者。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果发生这种情况只是为了重新观看之前的讲座
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个挑战中，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着更好地理解它们，然后继续前进。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，课程中的各个部分相互依存。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在从一节继续下一节之前，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要确保你完全理解是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该部分涵盖。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以休息一下，回顾一下我们写的代码，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查看你的笔记，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并查看我们在那段时间构建的项目化。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的话，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至应该尝试提出你自己的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了练习，自己写一些代码。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这样你才真正准备好继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下一节。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，如果您的代码有问题或错误，
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是从尝试自己解决错误开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对你的进步和你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习之旅。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为开发人员必须做的主要事情之一是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查找并修复我们也称它们的错误或错误。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在，如果你能解决问题，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后继续查看此处的 Q 和 A 部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Udemy 上，因为可能是其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前已经有同样的问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这也没有帮助，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你当然可以提出一个新问题。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此，请使用简短描述，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 codepen.io 上发布您的代码
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并在问答中分享链接。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要只是在问答中粘贴一堵代码墙，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，请使用 codepen.io 等服务。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想快速提一下我录制了这门课程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 Mac 上，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都会以完全相同的方式进行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Windows 或 Linux 上。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，如果您的计算机上出现问题，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是因为您使用的是不同的操作系统。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于到手了，你甚至可以说，最重要的是，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做这门课的时候玩得开心。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编码很有趣，看到它很有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己建造的东西。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果你因为某种原因感到沮丧，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后停止你正在做的任何事情，然后再回来。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说一次，
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是需要在编码和所有这一切的过程中获得乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此，让我们现在终于开始了。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now before leaving this Getting Started section,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let me give you eight quick considerations on how to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,actually take this course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I promise that they are a super short
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and super important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.96,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please, please, don't skip this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It will set you up for success with this course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So to start,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chances are that this is your very first contact
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with writing code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.04,0:00:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so please don't get overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have literally seen tens of thousands of students going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,through this course or one of my other courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I can tell you that it's 100% normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that in the beginning you will not really understand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just keep going through these first few sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't understand 100% at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you will very soon, believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't think something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess coding is not for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that thought is simply not allowed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also keep in mind that everyone has different learning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,speeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so you will get there eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just keep following the course
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and keep practicing as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now about actually taking the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always, always need to code along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is absolutely fundamental.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will learn exactly zero HTML and CSS skills by simply
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sitting there and watching me code.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you really have to actually write the code yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even if you're just typing the exact same words as I am
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,typing basically in a video, but it really doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're coding,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the code is getting into your brain and you're learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a course material to stick in your brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even better, then take notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So notes on code syntax, notes on theory concepts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and really notes on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take too many notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone has their own style.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So just find your own one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, try all the coding challenges that I present to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to do the best that you can,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if you get stuck for too long, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just go ahead and watch the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you have to try the coding challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise you will miss a lot of the learning opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here and also don't beat yourself up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you can't figure out the solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again, this is completely normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,especially if you're just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if that happens just to rewatch the lectures that were
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.84,0:03:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,covered in that challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,try to understand them a bit better and then move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the sections in the course build on one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so before moving on from a section to the next one,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,really make sure that you understand exactly what was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,covered in that section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So take a break, review the code that we wrote,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,review your notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and also review the projects that we built in that section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If there was any,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you should even try to come up with your own examples and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,write some code on your own in order to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And only then you are really ready to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the next section.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you have a question or an error in your code,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,always start by trying to solve the error by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is absolutely essential for your progress and your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,learning journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because one of the main things that a developer has to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to find and fix errors or bugs as we also call them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you can solve the problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then go ahead and check out the Q and A section here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on Udemy, because probably someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,already had the same problem before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that also doesn't help,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then of course you can ask a new question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, use a short description,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,post your code on codepen.io
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and share the link in the Q&amp;A.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So don't just paste a wall of code into the Q&amp;A,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, please use a service such as codepen.io.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to quickly mention that I recorded this course
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on a Mac,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but everything is going to work the exact same way on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Windows or on Linux.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if something doesn't work on your computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's not because you're using a different operating system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now finally hand, you can say even most importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have fun while doing this course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coding is a lot of fun and it's so rewarding to see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,something that you have built yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So if for some reason you're feeling frustrated,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then just stop whatever you're doing and come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So again,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you always need to have fun while coding and with all this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,being said, let's now finally get started.